---
title: Carb Smart Brie, Chicken and Apple Salad with Honey-Blueberry Dressing
description: Creamy brie, crunchy walnuts, sweet apples, hearty chicken and savoury croutons — all of your favourite salad toppings in one meal! A drizzle of honey-blueberry vinaigrette will send this salad over the edge.

